Emerson A. Phelps, Respondent v. The Metropolitan Elevated Railway Company, et al., Appellants. Decided January 11, 1892. Appeal by defendants from judgment entered upon the report of a referee. Davies & Rapallo, attorneys, and J. C. Thomson of *494counsel, for appellants. Edwin M. Felt, for respondent.

Before Freedman, P. J., McAdam and Gildersleeve, JJ.

Opinion by McAdam, J.; Freedman, P. J., and Gildersleeve, J., concurred.

Judgment affirmed, with costs.
